<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比和他的兄弟姐妹们走回了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到目前为止一切如常。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你希望发生什么有趣的事情？”潘瑟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不在乎是什么事情。”鲍比耸耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们到家的时候，玛莎阿姨正要出门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要去趟银行。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们能和你一起去吗？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“简！”鲍比嘘了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想等着自己的愿望成真。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”玛莎阿姨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后， 我们去给兰姆买新鞋子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鞋子？”鲍比几乎叫出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一天听上去确实没什么好玩儿的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们和玛莎阿姨一起去了银行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比没精打采地拖着脚走在最后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>银行的警卫迎接了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，各位。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好。”他们回应说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天早上银行里相当忙碌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨抱着兰姆去排队了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以在长椅这等我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她告诉孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们在木头椅子上坐下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比看到了那个店主，基弗先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还看到了贝克尔先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比又朝银行外面看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝尔克先生的狗西尔弗被拴在了一个消防栓上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，四个男人在银行门前停下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看上去很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人的脸上有道伤疤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个则扎着马尾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在想他们是不是丢东西了。”鲍比大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们就快的像闪电一般拉下了戴在头上的面具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比张大了嘴，但却什么也说不出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那几个男人拿着枪走进了银行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“女士们，先生们！”一个男人平静地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>银行里的顾客都转过身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们看到那些带着面具的男人时，有人开始尖叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“各位，请保持冷静。不要尖叫！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人举起了枪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，另一个男人把警卫的双手绑在了背后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嘴上也贴上了胶带。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个的男人锁上了银行的大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他快速拉下了每扇窗子的百叶帘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第四个男人则跳到了出纳员的身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别按警铃！”他警告他们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望每个人都到这里来。”第一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着孩子们坐的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，趴到地上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拜托，这里有孩子。”一个女人叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是玛莎阿姨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“安静！”第一个男人大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他可能是老大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果他们听话，”他转过去看着巴斯家的孩子们说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就不会有人受伤的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都听从了这些强盗的指令。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走到孩子们坐着的地方，然后趴在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨打手势让孩子们也趴在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比在地板上只能看到强盗们的脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有两个男人穿着运动鞋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其中一只运动鞋上有个大洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比可以看到那个男人穿的袜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是红蓝杠的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把你们的钱和首饰都放到这个袋子里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>穿着红蓝杠袜子的强盗在人们面前扔下了一个袋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们掏出了自己的钱包和皮夹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些取下了自己的手表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>强盗们还拿走了戒指、项链和耳环。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比微微抬起了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在柜台后面，出纳员打开了他们的存钱柜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点。”第四个男人说着拿枪靠近了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么样，鲍比？”赛伊对着他低声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的愿望成真了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>